Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.31,0:00:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.51,0:00:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.52,0:00:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.63,0:00:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.84,0:00:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.64,0:00:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.92,0:01:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.03,0:01:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.67,0:01:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.84,0:01:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[零式系统]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是把战况里出现的一切资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.05,0:01:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在即时运算后\N得出的庞大预测值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.05,0:01:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接反馈给驾驶员的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.42,0:01:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶舱系统的俗称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.46,0:01:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这系统甚至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.46,0:01:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会把驾驶员赶进极端状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.13,0:01:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实现完美的胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.57,0:01:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果连自己的死也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.64,0:01:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界变得混沌的时代里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.18,0:01:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在了令人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.44,0:01:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为最强兵器的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是飞翼零式和次代钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.32,0:02:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十七话\N[零式VS次代]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样一直飞去山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要及时赶到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人…我的敌人在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战略上失去优势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战术层面最大功效确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?增援还没来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令，敌人的战斗力仍未灭弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开战线的士兵增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在撤退比较好吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.65,0:03:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!如果就此撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.99,0:03:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会成为贵族的笑柄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，对手是钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们才更要打倒那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.36,0:03:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,财团不认同钢弹这名称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的第42 MD空降师团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会变成只是被一部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.64,0:03:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无名的机动战士歼灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.11,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人机动战士前来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战术层面处理完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续转到战略层面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用这部飞翼零式能战到哪地步?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.12,0:04:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起敌人，问题是自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飞翼零式吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗层面，目标确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.71,0:04:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.99,0:04:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算挑战这部飞翼零式吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.61,0:05:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯\N你选择了那机体是错误的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!我要确认战况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是敌人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问零式吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.05,0:05:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战情如何?\N山克王国怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.19,0:06:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国崩溃了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来迟一步了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.77,0:06:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，这场战斗有何意义?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟有何意义?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.45,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讲得没错啊  零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，我就做一名单纯的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你的宿命之战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天就在这里决一胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.67,0:06:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始终无法联络到第42 MD空降师团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?\N派MD登陆部队增援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人机动战士确定了有两部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对付他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.11,0:07:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要投入十倍的战斗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要多少奶和砂糖?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想迪尔麦优侯爵很快就会来到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你愈来愈怀念灭亡的祖国吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是从我的庭罢园里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,采摘茶叶而成的红茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.89,0:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许不合你口味\N但希望你饮用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.36,0:07:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不须要这样款待我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.09,0:07:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我向你们投降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.37,0:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指你适合被关进监牢吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们保护了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保护?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直渴望和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.98,0:08:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我们过去也才支援你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，你的周围集结了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.89,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从前背叛OZ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和卫星的叛乱份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.03,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们践踏了你的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.63,0:08:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了保护你的理想\N才救你出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世人会把今次山克王国的纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.91,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理解成那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你向全世界宣布的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和科主义既崇高又美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到了很多人的共鸣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我们为了保护那主义战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.63,0:08:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种事情应该无人会相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，他们会相信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为罗姆斐拉团会把它的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为财团的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.11,0:09:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做财团的代表?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我?\N没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.05,0:09:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.91,0:09:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团会藉着全面拥立你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而得到全世界的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们统一地球的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就会成为事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.06,0:09:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然\N这须要你和我们的合作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯成为财团的代表吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，你已经不是公主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就称你为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.34,0:09:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在世界最高处的莉莉娜女王吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以出卖为了和平而战的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个地球上能得到的最高地位\N就在你眼前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不须那种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想毫不羞耻地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.96,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在被压迫的人的悲伤之上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我们不同的只是方法论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.70,0:10:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们和你也渴望\N没有战斗的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你慢慢考虑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为还有时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.42,0:10:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，请你不要忘记这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你犹豫的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.29,0:10:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渴望和平的人会继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人会继续死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢!好慢啊!次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超越他的反应速度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飞翼零式!让我看见胜利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一招决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工程效率提升了20%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工程即将完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.69,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星居民的大量增员果然有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是君主政治支配的好处啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这么重要的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不须要什么自由平等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人讲得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西迪兹，我回去月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.75,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，请包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.47,0:13:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来还在使用有人机吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该有命令你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那些人员派去战舰工作班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不能浪费战力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.81,0:13:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是叛变的战力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你坐好，特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们究竟…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们从前被称为特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.99,0:13:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但今后就称为\N卫星的革命斗士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,革命?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.60,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们并非想取特校你的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星居民不希望杀戮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.14,0:14:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你们停止压迫就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是热狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羊已经走进栏里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[月亮女神革命]开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才的是什么爆炸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经占领这基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.63,0:14:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止无谓的反抗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是卫星的革命斗士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[白色獠牙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的同胞们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们站起来的时候终于来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以来压迫我们的兹巴洛夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在被我们的同志关起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.65,0:14:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经不须要再服从任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球贪婪地从我们身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夺去大量的劳力和资源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.06,0:15:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我们本来应该是平等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不用受任何人支配的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来吧，为了卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.47,0:15:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起建立宇宙的和平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.17,0:15:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于出手了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.61,0:15:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星又会跑进乱七八糟的战争里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些人真笨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.12,0:15:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们为何不杀我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.09,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有利用价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你今后在\N各个卫星的传媒上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宣布战败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而处决你方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.40,0:15:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们想待居民\N衷心希望时才执行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N那种做法和OZ没有分别啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切是从你们身上学回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,口吻十足特列斯的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.25,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别追!他逃不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这基地是我们的地盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.60,0:16:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的叛乱份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.30,0:16:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们以为我已经束手无策了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.17,0:16:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的MD\N会粉碎你们的阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特攻队叫首领
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基地周围没反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首领，MD启动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在于北面闸门交战中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.49,0:16:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.58,0:16:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了\N以这种装备毫无还手之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个宇宙希望战斗的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有邪恶意志的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都要全部消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!我们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,废话少讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.91,0:17:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹不是卫星的自己人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的MD不会战败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最终成为胜利者的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.07,0:17:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我和我的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.25,0:18:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧，我的MD是无敌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.59,0:18:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这个宇宙毫无敌手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是无敌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是贯彻我的正义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.08,0:18:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是月球基地镇压部队来的报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.38,0:18:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的反抗已经镇压了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，钢弹出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.12,0:18:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，好像是05的改良型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫怎样了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像被卷入那场战斗中死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?  没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我们的计划怎么办…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.64,0:19:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.94,0:19:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[月亮女神革命]只是刚刚开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.21,0:19:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘舰完成后，革命就会成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们看来都被机械摆布了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次代告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我选择的路上的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也认为那没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在北面B地点的海湾战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出动所有MD歼灭他们!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.25,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD登陆预定时间0450
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.39,0:19:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我驾驶飞翼零式进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去消灭海上的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部钢弹怎样处置?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是特列斯制造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能理解他的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的确会把次代交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.35,0:20:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本来打算选择和你不同的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在让我使用这部次代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.37,0:21:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.14,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.46,0:21:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你转告迪尔麦优侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.20,0:21:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特答应他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.03,0:21:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为罗姆斐拉财团的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.71,0:21:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就行了呢\N莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.16,0:22:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.61,0:22:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.61,0:22:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.61,0:22:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.61,0:22:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.11,0:22:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.61,0:23:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.11,0:23:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.61,0:23:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.61,0:23:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.81,0:23:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武装起来的卫星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.34,0:23:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自称[白色獠牙]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.74,0:23:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陆续攻陷OZ在宇宙驻守的重镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.01,0:23:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那漩涡里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.88,0:23:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔和诺茵\N继续找寻钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.22,0:23:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面
